Package: Rcaptext
Type: Package
Title: Text Analysis Tools for Capstone Projects
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Ric (Kernel236) 
Maintainer: Ric (Kernel236) 
Description: A comprehensive R package for text analysis and natural language processing,
    specifically designed for capstone projects. Provides functions for corpus loading,
    text cleaning, tokenization (unigrams, bigrams, trigrams), frequency analysis,
    coverage statistics, and visualization. Includes specialized tools for handling
    SwiftKey text corpora and exploratory data analysis of large text datasets.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
